Unfold the paper and fold it in half again, this time along the other diagonal. Cut along this fold, and unfold the paper. Repeat this process until you have a pile of paper triangles. Next, take one of the triangles and fold it in half along the longest side. Cut along the fold, and unfold the paper. Repeat this process with all of the triangles until you have a pile of folded paper pieces. Finally, arrange the folded paper pieces into a snowflake shape and glue them together. Voila! You've made a beautiful DIY paper snowflake.
